content.rendered:
Directed by Charissa Sanjarernsuithikul. Keesha Sharp. DeMane Davis.

Written by Nkechi Okoro.

Cast Bill Kelly (Tony Mallory). Azaria Carter (Teen Gabi). Kevin Howell (Police officer). Kelli Williams (Margaret). Brett Dalton (Trent). Gabrielle Walsh (Lacey). Karan Oberoi (Dhan). Arlen Escarpeta (Zeke). Anisa Nyell Johnson (Detective Shaker). Melody Williams (Grace). Tyler Merritt (Larry Evans). Art Newkirk (Detective Castillo). Shanita Wilburn (Journalist). Charlotte Ann Tucker (Sarah Holden). Ethan McDowell (Senator Holden). Alicia Cuthbertson (Detective). Trayce Malachi (Deron).

Language English.

Producers Shanola Hampton. Sonay Hoffman. Elizabeth Banks. Greg Berlanti. Lindsay Dunn. David Madden. Nkechi Okoro. Sarah Schechter.

Production Berlanti Productions. Brownstone Productions (II). Rock My Soul Productions.

No. of Seasons 1

No. of Episodes 11

Status OnGoing (2023–)
